# 📍 TryHackMe – Geolocating Images Write-up

This repository contains my solutions and methodology for the **Geolocating Images** room on **TryHackMe**.  
It demonstrates how to identify the location of images using OSINT techniques.

Room Link: https://tryhackme.com/room/geolocatingimages

---

## 🖼 Image Analysis & Answers

| Image | Answer | Method |
|-------|--------|--------|
| Image 1 | China | Google & Yandex reverse image search |
| Image 2 | Wrigleyville Sports | Observation + Google Maps |
| Image 3 | Meudon Observatory | Shodan (Used Shodan query: city:Meudon has_screenshot:true) & Google Maps |
| Image 4 | Abbey Road | Landmark recognition + Google Maps |

---

## 🔧 Tools Used

- **Google Reverse Image Search** – Visual matching  
- **Yandex Reverse Image Search** – Stronger visual recognition  
- **Google Maps** – Location verification  
- **Shodan** – OSINT for webcams and IoT devices  

---

## 🧠 Key OSINT Techniques Practiced

1. Reverse image search  
2. Visual clue analysis  
3. Map verification  
4. IoT & device intelligence (Shodan)  
5. Landmark identification  

